layout.text:
Welcome to Neptune’s Yard Prebiotic Fermented Seaweed Dog Food Supplement (400g). This innovative dog food supplement is provided by nature and perfected by science.

Seaweed has been used for millennia by coastal inhabitants as a nutritional, easily accessible and sustainable food source.
